{"tid":426973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環在線：永隆大客仔　10億做定存","createTime":"2017-10-07T06:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T08:05:36.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5116bd160f57fbfc16ba32b601a194a181a4f7e","tid":426973,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"香港真係好多有錢人，話說前排永隆銀行人民幣定期存款息率好鬼高，有位大戶因為咁搬咗筆巨款過去，零售銀行部主管鍾少權（Derek）話有成10億元人仔，係由另一間中小型銀行轉過嚟，息率幾多做幾長等等就唔可以透露。<br />\n<br />\n不過華華屈指一算，如果用10億人仔做一年定期存款，用返嗰時永隆最高4.55厘息計，一年賺4,550萬人仔，高過好多上市公司嘅每年盈利，真係名副其實嘅錢搵錢，一世唔使撈。<br />\n<br />\n財源滾滾來，加埋股市大旺，永隆佣金收入大升，唔怪得Derek上個月可以放心去西藏旅行，不過喺高海拔地方，肺活量十足嘅人好易有高山反應，所以Derek話要放慢個人咁行。不過佢話走嗰時大意漏咗張回鄉證，搞到心情有少少緊張，急急腳返去拎，即刻有輕微高山反應，「要唔要索返兩啖氧氣呀？」佢話保持心境平靜就OK。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20150514/19146610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20150514%2F19146610&d=C7tQ6xEAOqYXcbV8vwRrwrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=70b66729\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20150514%2F19146610&h=e613962b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20150514/19146610</a>"},{"pid":"023d3fb1674c8d8a8fed6c7090792da6d426eff7","tid":426973,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F&d=C7tQ6xEAOqYXcbV8vwRrwrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=32d1b03f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F&h=b37dcae8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/</a><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">20150514</span></strong></span>/19146610"},{"pid":"a68cb979db24eb816ee7f30c4aafd099a6c0c93f","tid":426973,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"16年支那幣趺到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00a77abe175fcd533e781efb45ce4c330861ff7","tid":426973,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>16年支那幣趺到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前排升番"},{"pid":"c5d150aee05b7eb3649f8ad4cb3071e5b204ea68","tid":426973,"uid":110988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:05:36.000Z","msg":"假如有五千萬  重好似誠哥咁日日返工  比人老點 比人撚狗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}